creator: The New York Times
description:
LibriVox recording of The Mounties in the News by The New York Times.
Read in English by Esther; David Lawrence
A newspaper account of the activities in the Western Canada during the Riel Rebellion, dating from August 1880 to January 1895. (Summary by David Lawrence)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
